  "title": "Connect* needs stories",
  "body": "**Feature: What is your use case for such a feature?**\r\n\r\nusing connect as a feature isn’t very easy, because the only example is a connectSearchBox.\r\n\r\n**Feature: What is your proposed API entry? The new option to add? What is the behavior?**\r\n\r\nadding stories or other examples about each of the connectors would be very useful in understanding how they work, and how you “should” use them. \r\n\r\n**What project are you opening an issue for?**\r\n- react-instantsearch",
